&lt;p>I&amp;rsquo;ve avoided this film all my life out of dread more than anything. It&amp;rsquo;s somewhat weird then that I watched this so early in my &amp;ldquo;Top 100&amp;rdquo; films quest. I knew I&amp;rsquo;d have to watch it eventually anyhow.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Japan: from miniature train to bullet train</title><link>https://www.davidbcalhoun.com/2013/japan-from-miniature-train-to-bullet-train/</link><pubDate>Tue, 29 Jan 2013 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.davidbcalhoun.com/2013/japan-from-miniature-train-to-bullet-train/</guid><description>&lt;figure itemprop="image" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/ImageObject" class="center">
